oji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再有咩唔開心 就喺到呻飽佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e9b30b8a1afbe706a72c16862fa6f84cc2e528","tid":1674393,"uid":246422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6e23ed633c1664b8064761eb15216f8f0cf679d3","tid":1674393,"uid":50306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"662c991dd585d1821fb08d295a017c30682308ab","tid":1674393,"uid":149575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:27:38.000Z","msg":"呢d情況同fd出黎飲舒壓下唔係好正常咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"失戀個陣有成日約出黎,但老豆單野得最fd個幾個先知,唔想成日煩到人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:40:09.000Z","msg":"我明你話唔想煩到朋友 <br />\n始終唔想成日放負<br />\n<br />\n但有需要都要講 想喊就喊<br />\n唔係嘅話再搵下社工傾計 <br />\n<br />\n曾經都好似你咁 最親嘅人發現有cancer <br />\n但又唔想影響返工同身邊人 呻幾句就算 <br />\n朋友都知安慰我講咩都冇用 都只可以聽我呻<br />\n久而久之就唔想成日講 <br />\n但件事過咗好耐之後 我問返個好朋友 個陣有冇覺得我煩？<br />\n佢話緊係唔會 只係佢冇發生過同樣嘅事唔知道點安慰我<br />\n其實心入面係好擔心 又冇理由叫我唔好講 叫我講多啲又驚我喊到收唔到聲<br />\n所以佢哋當初就只做聆聽者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外係 陪多啲老豆 唔好俾自己後悔<br />\n加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175120da611855391c39ae0af03e56c530e0f922","tid":1674393,"uid":325394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"撐住呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb98272395f91e35dbb65436b202585bc026f36","tid":1674393,"uid":50306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:40:33.000Z","msg":"多謝手足關心，昨晚老豆已走"},{"pid":"598aa9f1228879e952a7870beb1fad9b42b49c08","tid":1674393,"uid":6445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu